Opportunity Window Report

2024-11-11

Diagnostic Opportunity Window Report

This report summarizes the results of the bootstrapping change-point approach to select the diagnostic opportunity window. For this report we analyzed opportunity windows ranging from 10 to 100 days prior to the index diagnosis.

The following figure depicts the number of patients with any visit or an SSD-related visit each day prior to diagnosis:
